        public boolean isValidLetter(char let)
        This method check whether that character is valid DNA sequence character or not
        Overrides:
        isValidLetter in class Sequence
        Parameters:
        let - the character
        Returns:
        The method returns true if the character argument is equal to one of the eight characters ’a’, ’A’, ’c’, ’C’, ’g’, ’G’, ’t’ and ’T’. Otherwise, it returns false.
